---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Lucas Sommer — Everything I Know About Building Companies">

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "Lucas Sommer",
    "url": "https://lucassommer.com",
    "jobTitle": "Serial Entrepreneur",
    "description": "Serial entrepreneur and operator. Founded 8+ companies across marketing, construction, wine, fintech, and AI, with two acquisitions — now sharing everything he knows about building companies, free. Featured in Forbes, NBC News, and Entrepreneur.com.",
    "sameAs": [
      "https://twitter.com/lucasbsommer",
      "https://linkedin.com/in/lucasbsommer",
      "https://github.com/lucasbsommer"
    ],
    "alumniOf": {
      "@type": "CollegeOrUniversity",
      "name": "University of Miami"
    },
    "knowsAbout": ["Digital Marketing", "Construction", "Viticulture", "AI", "Entrepreneurship", "Fintech"],
    "award": ["WeMedia Pitch It! Grand Prize Winner", "Young Entrepreneur Council Member"]
  })} />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero container">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <span class="badge-dot"></span>
      Free to take
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">This is who I am. This is everything I know.</h1>
    <p class="hero-intro">
      I'm Lucas Sommer — fifteen years building companies, two exits, five running at once across marketing, construction, wine, fintech, and AI. This site is the whole download: the playbooks, the frameworks, the 239 ideas, the truths that actually moved the needle. No course, no paywall, no funnel. Take what's useful and go build something.
    </p>
    <ul class="hero-social">
      <li>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/lucasbsommer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
          Twitter
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/lucasbsommer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.5 2h-17A1.5 1.5 0 002 3.5v17A1.5 1.5 0 003.5 22h17a1.5 1.5 0 001.5-1.5v-17A1.5 1.5 0 0020.5 2zM8 19H5v-9h3zM6.5 8.25A1.75 1.75 0 118.3 6.5a1.78 1.78 0 01-1.8 1.75zM19 19h-3v-4.74c0-1.42-.6-1.93-1.38-1.93A1.74 1.74 0 0013 14.19V19h-3v-9h2.9v1.3a3.11 3.11 0 012.7-1.4c1.55 0 3.36.86 3.36 3.66z"/></svg>
          LinkedIn
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://github.com/lucasbsommer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z"/></svg>
          GitHub
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">8+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Companies Founded</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">2</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Acquisitions</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">15+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Years Building</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">400%+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Client ROAS</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story So Far -->
  <section class="container">
    <div class="story-bridge">
      <h2>The Story So Far</h2>
      <p>It started with a recording studio in my University of Miami dorm room. That turned into four music companies, then a marketing agency I grew to 13 people and sold. Along the way I planted a vineyard, got a general contractor's license, built a fintech platform, and drove results for brands like Netflix, Circle K, and Benchmade. I learned to run companies the hard way — by hand. Now I'm pointing all of it at one thing: AI agents that do the work — estimating construction jobs, running marketing, screening trades — so the companies run without me. <a href="/about">Read the full story &rarr;</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Everything I Know -->
  <section class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Everything I know</h2>
      <span class="section-meta">Free. No course, no funnel — take what's useful</span>
    </div>
    <div class="know-grid">
      <a class="know-card" href="/resources/ideation-flow">
        <span class="know-kicker">Framework</span>
        <span class="know-name">How to find a business worth building</span>
        <p class="know-desc">The exact filter I run every idea through — find the widest gap between what the market pays and what it costs you to deliver. Interactive worksheet included.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="know-card" href="/ideas">
        <span class="know-kicker">Idea bank</span>
        <span class="know-name">239 business ideas</span>
        <p class="know-desc">Every idea I've collected, vetted, or jotted down over the years — from full teardowns to one-line seeds. All free to steal.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="know-card" href="/about">
        <span class="know-kicker">Principles</span>
        <span class="know-name">8 Core Truths</span>
        <p class="know-desc">The operating principles I've tested across 8 companies, 2 exits, and 15 years. Every decision I make runs through this filter.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="know-card" href="/projects/monkey-business">
        <span class="know-kicker">Book</span>
        <span class="know-name">Monkey Business</span>
        <p class="know-desc">Why your brain is wired for survival, not building — and how to override the defaults. 20 chapters, from experience.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="know-card" href="/resources">
        <span class="know-kicker">Tools</span>
        <span class="know-name">Resources</span>
        <p class="know-desc">The tools and frameworks I've built or leaned on, collected in one place. Take them, use them, make them better.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="know-card" href="/map">
        <span class="know-kicker">Map</span>
        <span class="know-name">Where it all happened</span>
        <p class="know-desc">Every client, project, and place that shaped how I build — fifteen years across the country, on one interactive map.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Projects -->
  <section class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Projects</h2>
      <span class="section-meta">What I'm building and exploring</span>
    </div>
    <div class="projects-grid">

      <a class="project-card" href="/projects/carcin">
        <div class="project-icon" style="background:var(--status-building-bg); color:var(--status-building-text);">Ca</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-top">
            <div class="project-name">Carcin.ai</div>
            <span class="project-status status-building">Building</span>
          </div>
          <p class="project-desc">Fifteen years of agency work, productized. AI agents run strategy, execution, and reporting against a 103-channel framework — no account manager required.</p>
          <div class="project-tags">
            <span class="tag">AI</span>
            <span class="tag">Marketing</span>
            <span class="tag">SaaS</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="project-card" href="/projects/boss-pdx">
        <div class="project-icon" style="background:var(--status-exploring-bg); color:var(--status-exploring-text);">BP</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-top">
            <div class="project-name">Boss PDX</div>
            <span class="project-status status-active">Active</span>
          </div>
          <p class="project-desc">Licensed Portland GC, 17+ years. Custom homes, ADUs, commercial concrete, remodels — and a software layer that estimates jobs, writes the bid, and generates permit-ready plans automatically.</p>
          <div class="project-tags">
            <span class="tag">Construction</span>
            <span class="tag">Portland</span>
            <span class="tag">Operations</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="project-card" href="/projects/grove-vineyard">
        <div class="project-icon" style="background:var(--status-active-bg); color:var(--status-active-text);">GV</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-top">
            <div class="project-name">Grove Vineyard</div>
            <span class="project-status status-active">Active</span>
          </div>
          <p class="project-desc">Estate vineyard in the Chehalem Valley at 750ft elevation. Pinot Noir and Chardonnay crafted by Jacques Tardy, 8th generation Burgundian winemaker. Organic farming, Salmon Safe certified.</p>
          <div class="project-tags">
            <span class="tag">Wine</span>
            <span class="tag">Agriculture</span>
            <span class="tag">Willamette Valley</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="project-card" href="/projects/halem-heights">
        <div class="project-icon" style="background:rgba(168,85,247,0.12); color:#c084fc;">HH</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-top">
            <div class="project-name">Halem Heights</div>
            <span class="project-status status-active">Active</span>
          </div>
          <p class="project-desc">The estate wine brand and Airbnb side of the same Chehalem Valley land. Pinot Noir and Chardonnay by Jacques Tardy, distributed via Vinoshipper. Grove farms it; Halem Heights sells it.</p>
          <div class="project-tags">
            <span class="tag">Wine Brand</span>
            <span class="tag">Hospitality</span>
            <span class="tag">Willamette Valley</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="project-card" href="/projects/ad-apt">
        <div class="project-icon" style="background:rgba(124,58,237,0.12); color:#a78bfa;">Aa</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-top">
            <div class="project-name">Ad-Apt</div>
            <span class="project-status status-active">Active</span>
          </div>
          <p class="project-desc">Digital marketing agency delivering 400% ROAS for Payless, 7.2x ROAS for Teton Gravity Research, $1M+ new sales for True Blue Car Wash. Clients include Netflix, Circle K, Timberline Lodge, and Benchmade.</p>
          <div class="project-tags">
            <span class="tag">Agency</span>
            <span class="tag">Digital Marketing</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="project-card" href="/projects/intraalpha">
        <div class="project-icon" style="background:rgba(219,39,119,0.12); color:#f472b6;">IA</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-top">
            <div class="project-name">IntraAlpha</div>
            <span class="project-status status-exploring">Transitioning</span>
          </div>
          <p class="project-desc">Options-only trading platform with proprietary screeners, historical data going back 7 years, IV analysis, and daily algorithmic reports on 400+ stocks. Powered by ThetaData, TradingView, and Google Cloud.</p>
          <div class="project-tags">
            <span class="tag">Finance</span>
            <span class="tag">Algo Trading</span>
            <span class="tag">Discord</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a class="project-card" href="/projects/monkey-business">
        <div class="project-icon" style="background:var(--surface-2); font-size:1.35rem;">&#x1F412;</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-top">
            <div class="project-name">Monkey Business</div>
            <span class="project-status status-building">Writing</span>
          </div>
          <p class="project-desc">A book on the entrepreneurial mindset. Why your brain is wired for survival, not business — and how to override the defaults. 20 chapters, from experience.</p>
          <div class="project-tags">
            <span class="tag">Book</span>
            <span class="tag">Mindset</span>
            <span class="tag">Entrepreneurship</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Shipping Now -->
  <section class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Shipping now</h2>
      <span class="section-meta">Live systems, not slideware</span>
    </div>
    <div class="ships-grid">
      <a class="ship-card" href="https://plans.bosspdx.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <div class="ship-top"><span class="ship-name">Plans by Boss PDX</span><span class="ship-domain">plans.bosspdx.com</span></div>
        <p class="ship-desc">Turns a structured project spec into a full permit-ready construction submittal — cover sheet through structural calcs. A real Portland project already shipped through it.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="ship-card" href="https://estimate.bosspdx.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <div class="ship-top"><span class="ship-name">Estimate</span><span class="ship-domain">estimate.bosspdx.com</span></div>
        <p class="ship-desc">AI-assisted construction estimating. Scope goes in; a priced bid and a client portal come out.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="ship-card" href="https://carcin.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <div class="ship-top"><span class="ship-name">Carcin</span><span class="ship-domain">carcin.ai</span></div>
        <p class="ship-desc">An AI platform that builds and runs a small business's entire web presence. The agency, productized.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="ship-card" href="https://etf.intraalpha.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <div class="ship-top"><span class="ship-name">IntraAlpha ETF</span><span class="ship-domain">etf.intraalpha.com</span></div>
        <p class="ship-desc">Automated ETF research and tracking — screeners and daily reports, no analyst required.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="ship-card" href="https://ollage.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <div class="ship-top"><span class="ship-name">Ollage</span><span class="ship-domain">ollage.com</span></div>
        <p class="ship-desc">A discovery and editing platform for the things worth keeping.</p>
      </a>
      <a class="ship-card" href="https://skills.lucassommer.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <div class="ship-top"><span class="ship-name">Skills Editor</span><span class="ship-domain">skills.lucassommer.com</span></div>
        <p class="ship-desc">A UI for authoring Claude Code skills — the tooling layer under everything else here.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="ships-foot">Even this site is a system — built end-to-end in Claude Code.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>What Clients Say</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonials">
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <p class="testimonial-quote">"I have truly enjoyed working with your team. You've been brilliant."</p>
        <p class="testimonial-attr"><strong>Cheri Bernard</strong>, Sr. Manager Global Marketing — Payless ShoeSource</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <p class="testimonial-quote">"We have 12 lawyers and the phone rings daily with inquiries. I attribute that to the marketing we started with you which has grown over the last decade plus."</p>
        <p class="testimonial-attr"><strong>Ad-Apt Client</strong> — Law Firm</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <p class="testimonial-quote">"My whole internet marketing world changed after I used Ad-Apt. I literally trust them with my life and there is no one else I would want helping me online."</p>
        <p class="testimonial-attr"><strong>Ad-Apt Client</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Email Capture -->
  <section class="container">
    <div class="email-capture">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h3>Get updates</h3>
        <span class="email-meta">New projects, resources, and lessons shipped to your inbox.</span>
      </div>
      <form class="email-form">
        <input type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required />
        <button type="submit">Get updates</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Press -->
  <section class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Press & Recognition</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="credibility-highlights">
      <div class="cred-item cred-featured">
        <span class="cred-label">Award</span>
        <span class="cred-text">WeMedia Pitch It! Grand Prize Winner — $25,000</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cred-item cred-featured">
        <span class="cred-label">Speaking</span>
        <span class="cred-text">Guest Lecturer — Georgetown University, McDonough School of Business</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cred-item">
        <span class="cred-label">Member</span>
        <span class="cred-text">Young Entrepreneur Council (YEC)</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="press-bar">
      <span class="press-item">Forbes</span>
      <span class="press-item">NBC News</span>
      <span class="press-item">Entrepreneur.com</span>
      <span class="press-item">Reuters</span>
      <span class="press-item">Georgetown University</span>
      <span class="press-item">MarketingProfs</span>
      <span class="press-item">StartupNation</span>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ---- Hero ---- */
  .hero {
    padding-top: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Faint technical dot-grid behind the hero, masked to fade out */
  .hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: -2rem 0 0 0;
    z-index: -1;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, var(--border-hover) 1px, transparent 1.4px);
    background-size: 26px 26px;
    -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(42rem 26rem at 82% 18%, #000 0%, transparent 72%);
    mask-image: radial-gradient(42rem 26rem at 82% 18%, #000 0%, transparent 72%);
    opacity: 0.7;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--status-active-text);
    background: var(--status-active-bg);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.85rem 0.3rem 0.65rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .badge-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--status-active-text);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    line-height: 1.0;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    background: linear-gradient(168deg, var(--text-primary) 38%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent-text) 55%, var(--text-secondary)) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
  }

  /* Staggered entrance for the hero (specific children only — never the
     curator toolbar, which must stay hover-controlled) */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .hero-badge, .hero-title, .hero-intro, .hero-social, .hero-stats {
      animation: heroIn 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) both;
    }
    .hero-badge  { animation-delay: 0.02s; }
    .hero-title  { animation-delay: 0.09s; }
    .hero-intro  { animation-delay: 0.18s; }
    .hero-social { animation-delay: 0.27s; }
    .hero-stats  { animation-delay: 0.36s; }
    @keyframes heroIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }
  }

  .hero-intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-social {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .hero-social a {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .hero-social a:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }
  .hero-social svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--text-primary), color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent-text) 65%, var(--text-secondary)));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
  }

  .stat-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: 0.15rem;
  }

  /* ---- Section Headers ---- */
  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 4rem 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .section-meta {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  /* ---- Project Cards ---- */
  .projects-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .project-card {
    background: var(--surface-1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.35rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.15rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .project-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    background: var(--surface-2);
    color: inherit;
  }

  .project-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .project-body {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .project-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .project-name {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.2px;
  }

  .project-status {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
